</P>
<P>
 Antelope Valley 77, Mt. San Jacinto 36 -- The Marauders won their fourth 
consecutive game and stayed in a first-place tie in the Foothill Conference. It 
was never close as Antelope Valley led, 37-12, at halftime. 
