<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS: ACTING GENERAL MANAGER NAMED AT FAIR, EXPOSITION 
CENTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Becky Bailey-Findley has been appointed acting general manager for the Orange 
County Fair and Exposition Center in Costa Mesa. Bailey-Findley, deputy general 
manager for the Costa Mesa Fairgrounds, will assume the new post March 1. She 
succeeds Norbert Bartosik, who will become general manager of the California 
State Fair in Sacramento. 
