<TEXT>
<P>
 The man who trained TV's Flipper the dolphin collapsed and was rushed to a 
hospital Wednesday, the seventh day of his fast against the planned transfer of 
three dolphins to an Israeli amusement park. 
</P>
<P>
 U.S. dolphin expert Richard O'Barry collapsed at a Tel Aviv tent site, where 
