<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 3, 1994, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Southeast; Part J; Page 9 
