</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 2 New Macs Aimed at Education Market: Apple Computer Inc. introduced two 
all-in-one desktop Macintosh models intended for students and educators.The LC 
550 has a built-in monitor, stereo speakers, a microphone and a 33-megahertz 
68030 microprocessor. The LC 575 has all the features of the LC 550 but with a 
68040LC microprocessor and a built-in CD-ROM drive. The LC 550 retails for 
about $1,199 and the LC 575 sells for about $1,699. Apple may eventually sell 
the new Macintoshes to general consumers as well. 
</P>
