<P>
 Tri-Lite Lighting Inc.: The light fixture manufacturer and distributor said 
Wednesday that its subsidiary in Philadelphia has received a contract worth $3 
million to manage and maintain lighting systems at 515 Kmart stores in the 
Midwest. 
</P>
<P>
 Prolite Lighting Management Corp., the subsidiary, also is continuing 
discussions with Kmart that could result in a "considerably broader business 
relationship" between the two companies, according to Irvine-based Tri-Lite. 
Future work could include energy management and lighting retrofit 
installations. 
